{"tid":1439930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳7-11保安與警合作，籲市民購物要小心","createTime":"2019-08-10T09:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T09:55:43.000Z","uid":281029,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"08f1409d8e518ca4efef490614a94a8de9f4aa53","tid":1439930,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:21:42.000Z","msg":"[size=5][gold]<br />\n「逃犯條例」修訂爭議引發的運動持續，警察大規模搜捕成為另一焦點。<br />\n網上有消息流出，指7-11便利店的保安部已「和警隊合作」，警隊可取用多間7-11的閉路電視片段，而且7-11的閉路電視有錄音功能，故該消息呼籲大家購物時要小心，並直斥此舉「陷市民與七仔店舖經理與員工於不義」。<br />\n<br />\n網民直斥政府不斷製造「白色恐怖」，與民為敵，籲抗爭者要小心但更不能退縮。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：網上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S10HRaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS10HRaa.jpg&h=4621c32d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66179eaf980842809e00753531b47dc39ff7ba9d","tid":1439930,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:33:22.000Z","msg":"即係轉幫襯 circle K ?"},{"pid":"d5dfc207e026f38280b6fd69b063f6ad31d334a7","tid":1439930,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66179eaf980842809e00753531b47dc39ff7ba9d","tid":1439930,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:33:22.000Z","msg":"即係轉幫襯 circle K ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:35:12.000Z","msg":"難講，咁既時勢盡量唔好啦<br />\n出番大街，人多地方先好講"},{"pid":"6610cb436680ea7e8592da8c26e1623bf91ae4e0","tid":1439930,"uid":271407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e8252b2e3b68bde37c1980845200ab023173f9","tid":1439930,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66179eaf980842809e00753531b47dc39ff7ba9d","tid":1439930,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:33:22.000Z","msg"